nnoremap <C-q> :action Exit<CR>
nnoremap <leader>qq :action Exit<CR>
nnoremap <leader>qQ :action Exit<CR>

" ===================================
" Bookmarks
" ===================================
nnoremap <leader>mm :action ToggleBookmark<CR>
